# OS junk
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Safety net — the app's own shipsafe/.gitignore already covers these, but never
# let secrets or build artifacts into this public repo under any circumstance.
**/.env
**/.env.local
!**/.env.example
**/*.db
**/*.db-journal
**/node_modules/
**/.next/
**/tmp/
**/.scan-clones/
